      "content": "** **\n## Height [Read #\uD83E\uDDF1・high-ground for more]\n\n- **Early Height Take (8th Zone)**\nIf you take height early, make sure you have a lot of mats, as height can be costly when building up. A early heigh take doesn’t secure the win but most of the time if played right it can secure a top 5.\n\n- **How to take height Early**\nWhen taking height early, the only way to do it in this meta is to either get a good zone pull where you have natural elevation and can play off of it, or you can dash up to another team who is already in this position\n\n- **How to take height Late (10th Zone)**\nThe Most effective way to take heigh in 10th zone is to play second heigh and continue to spray up at height and try and damage them and ruin there mats. If you notice one of them gets knocked or cracked that can be a good time to push up. Another way to take heigh is if you have white heals you can playing in storm then chop them or take height from behind catching them by suprise\n\n- **Keep applying pressure**\nKeep spraying the people under you especially the person at 2nd height to prevent them from taking height",
